                <note rend="inline" type="source">875.6363/216: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Albania</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kodding</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tirana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-07-20T16:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 20, 1925—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 21—5:53 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>48. Ratification Standard Oil Company’s concession in Albania completed
                    yesterday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kodding</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
